    },
    {
      "time": 31.37,
      "time_str": "00:31.370",
      "text": "The Saturn 5 building up to 7.6 million pounds of thrust and it is cleared the tower.",
      "translation": "土星5号火箭产生760万磅的推力并离开了发射塔"
    },
    {
      "time": 38.02,
      "time_str": "00:38.020",
      "text": "This is Mission Control Houston, we are current have good 1st stage at this point.",
      "translation": "这里是休斯敦任务控制中心，目前第一级工作正常"
    },
    {
      "time": 43.54,
      "time_str": "00:43.540",
      "text": "（火箭引擎声）",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 50.09,
      "time_str": "00:50.090",
      "text": "Flight dynamics off to software, trajectory looks good. we show one half mile on altitude this time.",
      "translation": "飞行动力学软件状态良好，弹道正常，目前高度半英里"
    },
    {
      "time": 56.02,
      "time_str": "00:56.020",
      "text": "30 Houston go 30 seconds",
      "translation": "休斯敦，30秒"
    },
    {
