      "text": "（音爆）",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 60.0,
      "time_str": "01:00.000",
      "text": "Roll complete and we are pitching.",
      "translation": "滚转机动完成，正在进行俯仰机动"
    },
    {
      "time": 62.47,
      "time_str": "01:02.470",
      "text": "Roger that, standby for mode 1 throttle.",
      "translation": "收到，油门准备进入模式1"
    },
    {
      "time": 64.7,
      "time_str": "01:04.700",
      "text": "（音爆）",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 68.05,
      "time_str": "01:08.050",
      "text": "Mach 1 throttle, 1 throttle command. 1",
      "translation": "马赫，模式1油门指令"
    },
    {
      "time": 71.32,
      "time_str": "01:11.320",
      "text": "Altitude: 1.2 miles, velocity: 1500 feet per second.",
