    {
      "time": 76.27,
      "time_str": "01:16.270",
      "text": "Houston, what's story on Engine 5?",
      "translation": "休斯敦，5号发动机怎么了？"
    },
    {
      "time": 79.54,
      "time_str": "01:19.540",
      "text": "Jim, Houston. We don't have a story while inboard/outboard early, but the other Engines are go and you're go.",
      "translation": "吉姆，这里是休斯敦。我们之前没发现5号发动机的异常情况。其他的发动机能正常工作的话，继续执行任务"
